      "text": "Un tas Rehninsch Reka-\nbeams fuhtija Adoramu / kas\npahr to Mantu bija eezelts/ bet\nIsraëka Behrni nomehtaja to ar\nAkminieem/ ka tas nomirre. Bet\ntas Rehninsch Rekabeams kahpe\nsteigdamees us Ratteem/ ka tas\nus Jerusalemi behgtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta atkahpe tee Israëlteri\nno Dahwida Namma lihdscho-\ndeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XI. Vlodalla.\nRekabeams zaur weenu Praweetu atrahfs no\nKarra prett Jerobeamu : i / 3. Ustaifa un\napstiprina jawus Pilsfahtus eeksch Juhda :\n5. Uonemi tohs Preesterus un Lewitus/ kas\nno Jerobeama aisdsishti: 13. Apaemm\ndauds Seewas/ un dabbu ar tahm daud\nBehrnuß : 18.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N Rekabeams us Jeru-\nsalemi nahzis / lapulzi-\nnaja Juhda un Benja-\nmika Namunu fimts un astoz-\ndefmits tuhkstofchus jaunus us\nKarru tsmahzitus Wihrus/ prett\nIsraëlu karroht/ ka ta Walstiba\nattak Rekabeamam fkuhtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ta KUNGA Wahrdg\nnotikke us Semaju weenu Dee-\nta Wihru/ fazzidams:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Runna us Rekabeamn\nSalamaxa Dehlu/ to kehnixu\nno Juhda/ un us wiſfu Israëlu\neeksch Juhda un Benjaminna/ un\nfakki:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta farra tas KUNGS:\nJums ne buhs us augschu eet/\nneds prett juhseem Brahteem\nkarroht/ atgreeseetees ikkatrs fa-\nwä Namna/ jo fchi Leeta irr ne-\nmannim notifkusi. Un tee kla-\ntija ta KUNGA Wahrdus / un\ngreesahs atpakkat no ta Zetta\nprett Jerobeamu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rekabeams dsihwoja\nJerusaleme / un ustaifija tohe-\nPilsfahtus par Stiprumeem\neeksch Juhda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch ustaifija arridsan\nBetlemu/ un Etanu/ un Tekou.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Betzurn / un Soku /\nun Adullamn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gattu/ un Maresu/ un\nSiwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Adoraimu/ un Lachitu/\nun Aseku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Zaregu/ nn Ajalonu/\nun Eebrou/ kas eeksch Juhda un\nBenjaminna stipri Pilsfahtt bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darria schohs\nStiprumus wehl stipraks/ un\nlikke Ahwerstus eeksch teem / in\nMantas / Barribu / Etji un\nWihnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ikkurrd Pilsfahta likfe\nwiꞥſch preekschturramas Bru-\nras un Schlehpus/ un darrija\ntohs tohti stiprus / ta peederreja\nwiizam Juhda un Benjamins.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir tee Preesteri un Le-\nwiti/ kas starp wiſfu Israëln be-\nja/ atmahze pee wiſka no wiſ-\nfahm fawahin Robbeschahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee Lewitti vanette fa-\nwus Preeksch-Pilsfahtus un\nDsib-\n"
    }
